description:
A side-bag integrated inside the smaller leg unit unfolds together with the leg unit itself. Similar to the canopy segments the bag can be unfolded like a spanish hand-fan at around 30Â°.

Outside we the same fabrique like for the canopy (colors could be complementary) while inside we have strong inlay that cannot be easily damaged with a knife.

For security we provide a 3-digit code lock so that no keys need to be stored.

Inside the bag we provide several compartments for stuff like

- display adapters
- key chains
- power supply
- mouse and keyboard
- smartphone stand
- fidgets
- beverage
- food boxes
...
